dehydration and anxiety.

25:20.822 --> 25:22.824
So I'm gonna shoot over to his house.

25:22.824 --> 25:25.953
Keep the cameras outside and
hopefully have a chat with him.

25:29.779 --> 25:30.864
How are you, sir?

25:30.864 --> 25:32.393
- Come on in.
