25:43.668 --> 25:46.758
- [Brian] Eddie takes
advantage of my good nature.

25:47.891 --> 25:48.760
- [Gordon] Do you feel well enough

25:48.760 --> 25:50.029
to come back to the restaurant today?

25:50.029 --> 25:51.134
- Yeah.
- Good.

25:51.134 --> 25:52.708
