26:02.395 --> 26:05.284
The restaurant is the beating
heart of any good hotel.

26:05.284 --> 26:08.109
So the Keating has no
chance with chef Brian.

26:08.109 --> 26:10.601
Thankfully just a couple
of hours after I saw him,

26:10.601 --> 26:12.468
Brian is back at the hotel.

26:12.468 --> 26:14.590
- After going to the hospital,

26:14.590 --> 26:18.787
I believe the Gordon
is totally in my corner

26:18.787 --> 26:21.605
saying, get back in there,
get it, you got this guy.

26:23.427 --> 26:25.168
