the whole staff together

26:25.168 --> 26:28.244
to figure out how to get
this hotel back on track.

26:28.244 --> 26:29.777
Thank you all for at meet me.

26:29.777 --> 26:31.059
Am I happy to see you or what?

26:31.059 --> 26:32.404
How are you feeling more importantly?

26:32.404 --> 26:33.510
- I am feeling very good.

26:33.510 --> 26:35.595
- Brilliant, welcome back.
- Thank you.

26:36.753 --> 26:37.899
- Let's get everything out on the table

26:37.899 --> 26:38.921
'cause life's too short to fester.

26:38.921 --> 26:39.790
I'm here to help

26:41.674 --> 26:43.999
and I just wanna hear it from you guys.

26:43.999 --> 26:46.408
What's wrong with the Keating?

26:46.408 --> 26:48.514
- The resources, is the resources.

26:48.514 --> 26:49.463
I tell Eddie all the time,

26:49.463 --> 26:52.059
Eddie, I can't do my job.

26:52.059 --> 26:55.323
