should not be doing laundry,

26:55.323 --> 26:56.588
let me tell you that.

26:58.524 --> 27:01.705
The big concern I have
is the room service.

27:01.705 --> 27:04.749
How on earth did we get
ourselves in that mess?

27:04.749 --> 27:06.261
