27:16.699 --> 27:19.621
I tell you what I want and
you guys need to implement it.

27:21.391 --> 27:23.601
- Why is the menu so big?

27:23.601 --> 27:26.803
- Because Eddie comes up with ideas.

27:26.803 --> 27:27.991
Eddie sees things.

27:27.991 --> 27:29.576
Eddie has a lot of friends that come in

27:29.576 --> 27:32.058
