like to say no to me.

27:46.041 --> 27:47.490
- You have a general manager,

27:47.490 --> 27:49.471
you have a head chef, executive chef,

27:49.471 --> 27:50.952
you have a front desk manager,

27:50.952 --> 27:52.630
you shouldn't get involved.

27:52.630 --> 27:54.862
