27:54.862 --> 27:57.135
'Cause I have a vision here
and I give them the ideas.

27:57.135 --> 27:58.004
- No.

27:59.095 --> 27:59.964
No.

28:01.003 --> 28:03.277
- I cannot work with
you if you're like this.

28:03.277 --> 28:04.785
We have the key players.

28:04.785 --> 28:07.781
There's one little problem we have

28:07.781 --> 28:10.701
