28:14.200 --> 28:15.382
(dramatic music)

28:15.382 --> 28:17.499
- After last night,
dramatic turn of events.

28:17.499 --> 28:19.183
Look at me, Jesus Christ.

28:19.183 --> 28:21.347
The staff at the Keating have
finally found the courage

28:21.347 --> 28:23.589
to confront Eddie, the owner.

28:23.589 --> 28:26.300
Now there's one question I have to ask,

28:26.300 --> 28:28.958
tell me, who's the most
important person at the Keating?

28:28.958 --> 28:29.827
Who is it?

28:31.190 --> 28:32.257
Eddie, Brian, yeah?

28:33.296 --> 28:34.568
The most important person at the Keating,

28:34.568 --> 28:35.437
Sandra, who is it?

28:35.437 --> 28:36.792
- I got to say it's Eddie.

28:37.762 --> 28:40.564
- I mean, I believe it would be Eddie.

28:40.564 --> 28:41.669
- Eddie?

28:41.669 --> 28:42.879
- Sandra.

28:42.879 --> 28:44.206
- No, no.

28:46.971 --> 28:50.487
The most important person
at the Keating is the guest.

28:52.034 --> 28:54.758
