right, understand that.

29:10.563 --> 29:13.096
Eddie and Sandra, just come with me.

29:13.096 --> 29:14.671
If Eddie won't listen to me

29:14.671 --> 29:16.423
and he won't listen to his staff,

29:16.423 --> 29:17.684
maybe he'll listen to the people

29:17.684 --> 29:19.707
who could pay the bills around here.

29:19.707 --> 29:20.666
Eddie, up until now,

29:20.666 --> 29:22.418
this hotel has always been about you,

29:22.418 --> 29:23.774
your dream, your vision.

29:23.774 --> 29:25.403
Now, it's about the guest.

29:26.380 --> 29:27.778
I want you to meet some
very important people.

29:27.778 --> 29:29.328
