29:32.532 --> 29:34.884
- Hello, how are you?

29:34.884 --> 29:35.789
- Good.
- Fine.

29:35.789 --> 29:36.787
- Nice to see you.

29:36.787 --> 29:39.446
Guests that have been
staying at the Keating

29:39.446 --> 29:41.760
over the 24 to 48 hours.

29:41.760 --> 29:42.970
- Oh no.

