place back on the map.

30:01.801 --> 30:03.876
Give me your insights, please.

30:03.876 --> 30:05.910
What do you think of this luxury hotel?

30:06.796 --> 30:07.852
Madam, what you?

30:07.852 --> 30:10.998
- I walked into the room
and it smelled horrible.

30:10.998 --> 30:13.295
