little bit cheap and old.

30:19.617 --> 30:21.806
So it doesn't feel comfortable.

30:21.806 --> 30:22.906
- Madam, please.

30:22.906 --> 30:24.845
- I just feel like this place is designed

30:24.845 --> 30:26.899
kind of form over function.

30:26.899 --> 30:28.321
It was kind of weird.

30:29.318 --> 30:31.633
- Where's one supposed
to sit and eat breakfast

30:31.633 --> 30:33.281
in their room?

30:33.281 --> 30:35.001
My husband had to stand up this morning

30:35.001 --> 30:37.587
to have his breakfast
while I took the only chair

30:37.587 --> 30:38.995
and sat at the desk.

30:38.995 --> 30:40.434
- [Gordon] I'm sorry.

30:40.434 --> 30:41.855
- Our room service was,

30:42.811 --> 30:44.552
we ordered a couple of small pizzas

30:44.552 --> 30:46.753
and they essentially looked
like microwave pizzas

30:46.753 --> 30:47.858
and then the order was wrong.

30:47.858 --> 30:49.213
So we called to correct,

30:49.213 --> 30:51.351
they eventually you know brought
up what we actually ordered

30:51.351 --> 30:53.541
and then in the morning,
they charged us above.

30:53.541 --> 30:55.532
- [Gordon] Wow, I'm sorry, anybody else?

30:55.532 --> 30:57.305
- There was some really high end stuff

30:57.305 --> 30:58.347
and then at the same time,

30:58.347 --> 31:00.871
there was just simple
amenities that were skipped.

31:00.871 --> 31:01.945
- But are you saying there's better

31:01.945 --> 31:04.495
at the same price out there?

31:04.495 --> 31:05.625
- Yes.
- Sure.

31:06.939 --> 31:09.536
- Yeah, Eddie, your baby, your vision,

31:09.536 --> 31:10.794
on the back of that feedback.

31:10.794 --> 31:12.463
- No, I appreciate the feedback.

31:13.774 --> 31:16.063
- I have one question for you all,

31:16.063 --> 31:18.060
who would return here?

31:18.060 --> 31:20.875
Let's do a show of hands who
come back to the Keating.

31:22.924 --> 31:24.791
Wow, not one person

31:27.147 --> 31:29.712
- Gordon's comment about
it's not what I want,

31:29.712 --> 31:31.068
it's what the guests want.

31:31.068 --> 31:33.007
- Wow.
- I'm starting to realise

31:33.007 --> 31:35.690
that some of the things he's
saying actually are true.

31:36.907 --> 31:37.939
- I really apologise

31:37.939 --> 31:40.504
and I am looking forward to
having you guys in the future.

31:40.504 --> 31:43.392
I can tell you will have
a different experience

31:43.392 --> 31:46.917
- Eddie and Sandra, I'm not
trying to embarrass you,

31:46.917 --> 31:49.305
but this is for me critical feedback

31:49.305 --> 31:51.195
and it's only gonna get better.

31:52.589 --> 31:54.132
- The feedback from
the customers was good.

31:54.132 --> 31:56.489
I'm realising there's more
issues than I thought we had

31:56.489 --> 31:58.314
and just being here over
the past couple of days,

31:58.314 --> 31:59.346
I'm seeing what they are.

31:59.346 --> 32:01.463
I think we can definitely
fix them and streamline them

32:01.463 --> 32:03.131
so the place works a lot more efficiently

32:03.131 --> 32:04.549
and all the guests are happy.

32:04.549 --> 32:06.061
- Thank you, I appreciate it.

32:07.344 --> 32:09.700
Eddie is starting to see how
much things have to change

32:09.700 --> 32:11.121
for this place to succeed.

32:13.224 --> 32:14.809
