33:38.226 --> 33:41.135
- I love Eddie but I have
to be able to just say,

33:41.135 --> 33:42.605
this is not going to work,

33:42.605 --> 33:45.369
this is not to the benefit
of the hotel, the guests,

33:45.369 --> 33:46.828
the restaurant or anything.

33:46.828 --> 33:48.956
- [Gordon] You can do it
and I know you can do it.

33:48.956 --> 33:53.147
- I needed this too
remember what I used to do

33:53.147 --> 33:57.008
and that there is no limit to
what I can do in the future.

34:02.459 --> 34:05.900
- Brian and Eddie are both
making great strides and tonight,

34:05.900 --> 34:07.221
my design team will move in

34:07.221 --> 34:09.851
and try to get this hotel out of the pits.

34:09.851 --> 34:13.072
But first, there's something
just got to try it.

34:13.072 --> 34:14.116
I've got a 25 grand bath,

34:14.116 --> 34:15.922
