35:44.665 --> 35:47.042
- It's just such an emotional experience.

35:47.042 --> 35:51.495
- You all have a hand in
helping the guests feel welcome.

35:51.495 --> 35:52.412
- It's amazing.

35:52.412 --> 35:53.839
